---
description: Big Bang quote finder conventions
globs: "**/*"
---

- Monorepo root; Python path includes repo root for `apps.api` and `pipeline`
- Time fields in milliseconds
- Video source: local MKV/MP4 only; clips go to Supabase Storage bucket `clips`
- Secrets only in `deploy/.env`, never commit
- User has S01E01–E02 only for MVP
